             were indicted for <rs id="t18220911-274-off1443" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t18220911-274-off1443" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t18220911-274-off1443" type="offenceSubcategory" value="pocketpicking"></interp>
               stealing, on the <rs id="t18220911-274-cd1444" type="crimeDate">14th of August</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18220911-274-off1443 t18220911-274-cd1444"></join>, five mats, value 15 s., the goods of 
                     
                        <persName id="t18220911-274-victim2499" type="victimName">
                           James 
                           Piper
                        <interp inst="t18220911-274-victim2499" type="surname" value="Piper"></interp>
